# Fundamental messages
# ====================

_TaskName:NCRmgr
_SpriName:!ncrmgr
Version:0.01 (16 Feb 1999)
FullName:NC ROM manager

# Positions of useful resources
# =============================
#
# Repository - Position of the repository relative to the application
#              directory location, e.g. 'ADFS::4.$.!NCRmgr.' with the
#              value of this token appended to give the top level
#              repository directory.
# MountZip   - Command to issue to mount a Zip disc
# Zip        - Path to scan for ROM image files on a Zip disc

Repository:Repository
MountZip:IZipFS:Mount 0
Zip:IZipFS::0.$

# Export commands and messages
# ============================

Exporting:Exporting ROM image file to Zip disc, please wait...
Export1:Copy
Export2:IZipFS::0.$.
Export3: A~C~DF~L~N~P~Q~RS~T~V

# Import commands and messages
# ============================

ImportScan:Checking for space in the main repository, please wait...
ImportFull:The repository is full! Cannot import the ROM image file. You need to delete an unwanted item from the repository, then try the import again. Press space bar to continue.
Importing:Importing ROM image file from Zip disc, please wait...
Import1:Copy
Import2: A~C~DF~L~N~P~Q~RS~T~V

# Build commands and messages
# ===========================

BuildProgress1:Clearing files off Zip disc, please wait...
BuildWipe:Wipe IZipFS::0.$.* ~CFR~V
BuildCheck:<NCRmgr$Dir>.Programmer
BuildProgress2:Copying programmer software to Zip disc, please wait...
BuildCopy:Copy <NCRmgr$Dir>.Programmer.* IZipFS::0.$.* A~C~DF~L~N~P~QRS~T~V

# Errors
# ======

Format1:Warning - error %0:
Format2: "%0"
Format3:Query:

Continue:Press A to accept error and continue, or Q to quit.

NoMemGen:Insufficient free memory to continue this operation (%0)
ZLibErr:Error code %0 generated by compression / decompression engine

ROMFmt01:ROM image format error (no line feed found after "RPKG" header)
ROMFmt02:ROM image format error (no closing colon found after ID byte and comment)
ROMFmt03:ROM image format error (no line feed found after closing colon)

# Queries
# =======

DeleteZip:Are you sure you want to delete this file from the Zip disc?
DeleteMain:Are you really sure you want to delete this file from the main image repository?
CheckWipe1:Do you want to clear all files off the Zip disc before proceeding?
CheckWipe2:Are you sure you want to clear all files off the Zip disc?
CheckExport:Do you want to verify that the export was successful?
CheckImport:Do you want to verify that the import was successful?

